 group, which was formed among his best friends after graduating from a vocational high school. He made his acting debut in the film \"Class 952\" (九五2班) in 2016.\n\nOn September 15, 2018, Liu Yu Ning released his first solo single, \"Imagine.\" On March 25, 2019, he won the Best New Artist and the Internet Influence Honor awards at the Chinese Top Ten Music Awards 2019. At the Chinese Top Ten Music Awards 2020, he won the All-Round Artist of the Year award, the National Recommended Singer award, and the Media Recommended Album for his first studio album, \"Ten\".","name":"Liu Yuning","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"CN","iso_639_1":"zh","name":"普通话","english_name":"Mandarin","data":{"biography":"刘宇宁，1990年1月8日出生于辽宁省丹东市，中国内地流行乐男歌手、影视演员，摩登兄弟乐队主唱。\n\n2014年，担任摩登兄弟的主唱。2015年，随摩登兄弟入驻YY平台。2016年，主演个人首部电影《九五2班》，从而正式进入演艺圈。2017年，随摩登兄弟由室内转入街头直播；同年，其主演的犯罪悬疑电影《秦贼有道》上映。2018年，其主演的青春励志爱情电影《罗曼蒂克振兴史》上映 ；同年，出演个人首部影视剧《租界少年热血档案》；9月15日，推出首支个人单曲《想象》。2019年，成为湖南卫视音乐竞技节目《歌手2019》首位“全民举荐踢馆歌手”。","name":"刘宇宁","primary":true}},{"iso_3166_1":"TW","iso_639_1":"zh","name":"普通话","english_name":"Mandarin","data":{"biography":"","name":"劉宇寧","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"RU","iso_639_1":"ru","name":"Pусский","english_name":"Russian","data":{"biography":"","name":"Лю Юй Нин","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"VN","iso_639_1":"vi","name":"Tiếng Việt","english_name":"Vietnamese","data":{"biography":"Lưu Vũ Ninh là một diễn viên, ca sĩ Trung Quốc và là ca sĩ chính của nhóm nhạc Modern Brothers. Năm 2018, anh chính thức debut, bắt đầu sôi nổi tham gia các hoạt động ca hát và diễn xuất.","name":"Lưu Vũ Ninh","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"KR","iso_639_1":"ko","name":"한국어/조선말","english_name":"Korean","data":{"biography":"","name":"류우녕","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"HK","iso_639_1":"zh","name":"普通话","english_name":"Mandarin","data":{"biography":"劉宇寧，1990 年 1 月 8 日出生於遼寧省丹東市，中國內地流行樂男歌手、影視演員，摩登兄弟樂隊主唱。\n\n2014 年，擔任摩登兄弟的主唱 。2015 年，隨摩登兄弟入駐 YY 平台 。2016 年，主演個人首部電影《九五 2 班》，從而正式進入演藝圈 。2017 年，隨摩登兄弟由室內轉入街頭直播 ；同年，其主演的犯罪懸疑電影《秦賊有道》上映 。2018 年，其主演的青春勵志愛情電影《羅曼蒂克振興史》上映 ；同年，出演個人首部影視劇《租界少年熱血檔案》 ；9 月 15 日，推出首支個人單曲《想象》 。2019 年，成為湖南衞視音樂競技節目《歌手 2019》首位“全民舉薦踢館歌手” 。","name":"劉宇寧","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"FR","iso_639_1":"fr","name":"Français","english_name":"French","data":{"biography":"Liu Yuning, né le 8 janvier 1990 à Dandong, Liaoning, est un chanteur et acteur chinois, leader du groupe Modern Brothers. Issu d’un milieu modeste, il se lance dans la musique via des performances de rue et des lives sur YY et Douyin, gagnant en popularité en 2018. Il débute comme acteur dans le film Class 952 (2016) et joue dans des séries comme Hot-Blooded Youth (2019), The Legend of Anle et The Prisoner of Beauty (2025). Son premier single solo, Imagination (2018), marque ses débuts musicaux. Récompensé aux Chinese Top Ten Music Awards, il est nommé dans Forbes China 30 Under 30 (2019).","name":"Liu Yuning","primary":false}}]}},"person_117654_translations":{"at":1772471560198,"data":{"id":117654,"translations":[{"iso_3166_1":"US","iso_639_1":"en","name":"English","english_name":"English","data":{"biography":"David Sterne (born 1946) is an English actor. He has appeared in more than 90 films since 1973.\n\nAfter leaving the British Army, Sterne trained at the Webber Douglas Academy of Dramatic Art. A former member of the Royal Shakespeare Company.  He has worked in television, film and radio for over 40 years. He is most recognised for his portrayal of Larry Bishop in the BBC's 'Detectorists', and more recently as Tom Thomas in three seasons of Britbox's 'The Sister Boniface Mysteries'. His mentor was Lindsay Anderson (Director of \"If...\" & \"O Lucky Man!\"). His daughter is Rachel Stone, an Associate Producer with Hartswood Films UK.","name":"David Sterne","primary":true}},{"iso_3166_1":"KR","iso_639_1":"ko","name":"한국어/조선말","english_name":"Korean","data":{"biography":"","name":"데이비드 스턴","primary":false}}]}},"movie_1261188_credits":{"at":1772471561016,"data":{"id":1261188,"cast":[{"adult":false,"g